Indian Premier League (IPL) bụ asọmpi egwuregwu cricket nke ụmụ nwoke, nke otu iri na-asọ mpi n'ime obodo iri India. Ndi Board of Control for Cricket in India (BCCI) hibere otu a na 2007.

IPL bụ asọmpi cricket kacha elele n'ụwa ma na 2014 ọ nọ n'ọkwa nke isii site na nkezi ndị bịara asọmpi niile. N'afọ 2010, IPL ghọrọ mmemme egwuregwu izizi n'ụwa ka a na-agbasa na YouTube. Uru nke ika IPL na 2019 bụ ijeri US$6.3
Enwere oge iri na anọ nke asọmpi IPL
Ndị ji aha IPL ugbu a bụ Chennai Super Kings, na-emeri oge 2021.
